    <step order="5">Implement `InjectDocumentContextAsync`: retrieve document via SpeFileStore, extract/chunk text, count total tokens</step>
    <step order="6">Implement the budget check: if total tokens &lt;= 30K inject all; if &gt; 30K implement conversation-aware re-selection using embedding similarity to latest user message</step>
    <step order="7">Implement cosine similarity scoring and greedy chunk selection up to the 30K token budget limit</step>
    <step order="8">Add logging for metadata only (document ID, chunk counts, tokens used) — MUST NOT log chunk text per ADR-015</step>
    <step order="9">Wire `DocumentContextService` into `SprkChatAgentFactory` using factory instantiation (not DI registration); wire into `PlaybookChatContextProvider` so chunks are appended to system prompt</step>
    <step order="10">Run `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` — verify no build errors</step>
    <step order="11">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change task R2-011 status to completed (🔲 → ✅)</step>
  </steps>

